This is the English translated version of my hentai comic Pirates VS Ninjas 5, the fifth installment of this hentai and humor parody of One Piece, Naruto, and Fairy Tail.

This translation has been made possible thanks to the support on Patreon and Subscribestar.

www.patreon.com/c/natsumemetalsonic
https://subscribestar.adult/natsumemetalsonic

There I will continue translating the rest of the comics in the collection and drawing new ones. If you want to support me there, I will be grateful.
